data.description: Charming townhome with 3 beds and 2.5 baths in Randleman. Main floor features a spacious open floorplan and a foyer with hardwood floors that span throughout the dining room and kitchen, providing a seamless flow and an elegant ambiance. Kitchen has solid surface countertops, lots of cabinetry and counterspace, tasteful kitchen backsplash and plenty of storage with the under the stairs pantry. Home boasts 9' ceilings, crown molding, and tile in bathrooms. Delightful private patio space where one can unwind after a long day. Assigned parking spots right out front of the unit and low HOA dues. Situated close to I-73 and only minutes from shopping, entertainment, and restaurants.
